<comment><![CDATA[Stores registered users of the Orac system.
Each record represents a unique user identity, along with their display name, contact details, and active/inactive status.
Includes audit columns for creation/update tracking and a row_version field for optimistic locking.
Key uses: Controls ownership of conversation history, preferences, and other user-specific settings.]]></comment>
