<comment><![CDATA[user_id — Primary key for the orac.users table.
Generated automatically by Oracle on insert (generated always as identity).
Used as a foreign key from orac.user\_preferences.user\_id and orac.context\_history.user\_id to relate preferences and conversation turns to a user.
Immutable once created and never reused.
]]></comment>
