<comment><![CDATA[username — Unique login handle for the orac.users table.
Type varchar2(100) not null.

Purpose: stable, human-readable identifier used in UIs, APIs, and audit defaults (preferred over email for identity).
Change policy: should rarely change; foreign keys are unaffected (they use user_id), but external systems may cache it.
Validation: not enforced in DDL; recommend restricting to a safe set (e.g., letters/digits/._-) and trimming whitespace in the application.
Case: treat consistently in the application (decide on case sensitivity and normalize accordingly).]]></comment>
