<comment><![CDATA[display\_name — Human-friendly name for the user (orac.users).

Purpose: shown in UIs, greetings, and reports; not used for authentication or joins.
Not unique; multiple users may share the same display name.
If null, the application should fall back to `username`.
Change policy: user-editable; updates do not affect foreign keys (they use `user_id`).
Validation: trim whitespace; allow Unicode; avoid storing sensitive info beyond what the user intends to display.
]]></comment>
