<comment><![CDATA[email — Primary contact email for the user (orac.users).

Purpose: notifications, account recovery, and admin contact; not used for joins (foreign keys use user_id).
Uniqueness: not enforced in DDL; make it unique only if your app requires one-account-per-email.
Validation: enforce format and domain checks in the application; consider a verified flag and timestamp elsewhere.
Case: treat comparisons as case-insensitive; store a normalized lowercase copy for lookups.
Privacy: PII—restrict access, avoid logging, and consider encryption-at-rest if policy requires.]]></comment>
